6 WHEREAS, Kevin Kresse said that after a career in advertising,
7 "Sculpture came back in my life when I started teaching drawing [and]
8 painting at the Arkansas Arts Center. I sat in on figure sculpting classes,
9 doing clay work . . . I went back to UALR and learned bronze casting with
10 Michael Warrick. But honestly, both painting and sculpting, I learned in the
11 studio through trial and error"; and
