13 WHEREAS, Kevin Kresse has created busts of legendary Arkansas musicians
14 Levon Helm and Al Green as well as the Breaking the Cycle sculpture at
15 Riverfront Park in Little Rock and the Mother Earth fountain sculpture at
16 North Little Rock's Argenta Art Park; and
17
18 WHEREAS, Kevin Kresse also paints, and has completed murals including
19 the Dogtown Proud mural in the Argenta neighborhood of North Little Rock; and
20
21 WHEREAS, Kevin Kresse has exhibited his work around Arkansas as well as
22 in Memphis, Tennessee, Atlanta, Georgia, New York City, New York, and
23 Washington, D.C.; and
24
25 WHEREAS, Kevin Kresse has earned acclaim for his work, including
26 receiving the Governor's Art Award for Individual Artist in 2015 and being
27 selected in 2016 by the Mid-America Arts Alliance for a painting fellowship
28 and as one (1) of only four (4) artists to represent the Alliance at the
29 fiftieth anniversary of the National Endowment for the Arts; and
