31 WHEREAS, Kevin Kresse said of being selected to create the statue of
32 Johnny Cash, "As far as my career, this was the biggest stage so far. I
33 really wanted to get Johnny right technically, but also get Johnny's
34 qualities of humbleness and soulfulness into the piece as well . . .
35 Sculpting Johnny Cash for the U.S. Capitol is such an incredible honor . . .
36 I felt quite a bit of a responsibility to kind of represent Arkansas and say
